.DT
testchar
Discworld creator help
testchar

.SH Name
.SI 5
testchar
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
testchar <player> {on|off}
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command can be used to mark a player as a creator test character, or to
remove a test character's test character status. It adds the "no score",
"no delete" and "test character" properties to the victim.

The character you are making into a test character must be logged on at the
same time.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> testchar taffytest on
Taffytest is now a test character.
> testchar taffytest off
Taffytest is no longer a test character.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
.EP

